WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:07.120
How many of you can feel that something major is about to come?

00:00:07.480 --> 00:00:08.859
That's what I heard in the spirit.

00:00:08.859 --> 00:00:14.240
How many of you are awake and know that something major is about to come?

00:00:14.240 --> 00:00:22.470
Do you feel it inside?

00:00:22.480 --> 00:00:24.1000
How hungry are you?

00:00:26.259 --> 00:00:28.015
He says, 'How bad?

00:00:28.015 --> 00:00:32.719
How much do you want to see the glory?

00:00:32.719 --> 00:00:37.200
' Do you hear him?

00:00:37.200 --> 00:00:39.220
He said, 'How bad, how hungry, how desperate?

00:00:39.400 --> 00:00:40.756
Do you want to see the glory?

00:00:40.756 --> 00:00:52.950
How much do you want to see the glory daily?

00:00:52.960 --> 00:00:56.640
' Leave the old things behind.

00:04:42.080 --> 00:04:45.199
Multitudes will come.

00:04:55.680 --> 00:05:16.840
He says the multitudes will come as you come up higher with my fire, walking in your authority.

00:05:26.987 --> 00:05:29.653
Working and walking with your authority.

00:06:04.000 --> 00:06:08.720
I'm in the Swiss Alps, and I'm going into the towns.

00:06:09.008 --> 00:06:18.469
I can see myself knocking on the door of each one of those little places, alerting them that a great revival is about to be upon them.

00:06:25.840 --> 00:06:29.600
We're going through Europe right now.

00:06:29.600 --> 00:06:31.680
It's a march.

00:06:35.350 --> 00:06:41.680
I hear him leading the people and it's 'follow the leader' through the towns in Europe.

00:06:44.560 --> 00:06:50.319
We're knocking on the door of the heart of the unbeliever.

00:06:50.586 --> 00:06:56.880
As we knock on the heart of the unbeliever, I see we're marching in a single-file line.

00:06:57.360 --> 00:07:02.400
The Lord Jesus Christ is leading the charge.

00:07:03.280 --> 00:07:09.244
He knocks on the door, and whenever they open it, they get in line and follow the leader.

00:07:11.280 --> 00:07:18.183
Following the leader, he's saying whatever I hear in the spirit as they're marching down the road.

00:07:18.183 --> 00:07:21.580
They're marching down the road, and he's saying, 'Come with me.

00:07:21.580 --> 00:07:22.390
Come up higher.

00:07:22.390 --> 00:07:27.919
' Jesus is moving throughout Europe, moving throughout the villages and knocking.

00:07:35.040 --> 00:07:40.160
As he knocks on the door of the hearts of the unbeliever, they follow in line.

00:07:41.200 --> 00:07:49.028
The line is getting longer, for he's calling the souls of men.

00:07:49.028 --> 00:08:11.885
And this is the mission.

00:08:12.216 --> 00:08:17.589
You must know your authority.

00:08:17.599 --> 00:08:22.560
He's knocking on hearts throughout the world.

00:08:23.680 --> 00:08:34.747
The time is late.

00:08:35.813 --> 00:08:48.070
He says the time is late.

00:08:58.994 --> 00:08:59.269
Now he's going throughout South America and Australia.

00:08:59.269 --> 00:09:03.466
There is no longer a day; the time is short.

00:09:34.535 --> 00:09:40.630
You must get on the boat.

00:09:40.640 --> 00:09:45.279
There is no longer a day.

00:09:49.817 --> 00:09:54.080
He's talking about the timeframe in the spirit realm.

00:10:08.399 --> 00:10:31.110
The sun is setting.

00:10:38.560 --> 00:10:44.926
He's adding to the body, one day at a time.

00:10:44.926 --> 00:10:47.920
He's bringing the people in.

00:10:49.930 --> 00:10:53.252
It's like a march, and Jesus is leading the march.

00:10:54.959 --> 00:10:59.795
I see he has a drum in his hand.

00:10:59.795 --> 00:11:02.639
He's drumming again and again.

00:11:03.359 --> 00:11:12.444
I like to look at it.

00:11:20.160 --> 00:11:25.360
He's adding the people, knocking on the hearts of men.

00:11:30.480 --> 00:11:33.211
It doesn't matter how big you think you are.

00:11:37.887 --> 00:11:41.618
From celebrities to the poorest of the poor, he's bringing us all in.

00:11:42.187 --> 00:11:44.320
He has such great things in store.

00:11:47.154 --> 00:11:58.870
For the greater works you will do, he will work through you.

00:11:58.880 --> 00:12:05.279
Days of fun have just begun, bringing in the harvest.

00:12:08.000 --> 00:12:15.030
