I see houses that have cobwebs on them, houses full of darkness, and he's knocking on their door.

00:12:29.371 --> 00:12:36.240
The ones that people had forgotten, the unlovely.

00:12:39.086 --> 00:12:52.275
There are cobwebs on the doors of these houses, and they look spooky, but he said, 'People have forgotten them, but I have not forgotten them.

00:12:52.275 --> 00:13:00.870
' He's knocking on the door, calling them in.

00:13:09.920 --> 00:13:10.373
He's calling in everyone, even those in the darkest of sin.

00:13:10.373 --> 00:13:29.630
'They will know my son,' he says.

00:13:37.519 --> 00:13:50.959
Ask the Holy Spirit to help you become a greater witnessing tool for him, a mouthpiece, so that he can flow within.

00:13:53.849 --> 00:14:10.310
You add to the march of the beat, and they will bring them to their knees.

00:15:24.354 --> 00:15:28.256
