00:39:28.696 --> 00:39:39.370
I see the people hiding in their bunkers.

00:39:41.200 --> 00:39:58.302
I see the face of the man over Facebook, and he is trembling in a bunker.

00:39:58.302 --> 00:39:59.404
No bunker will hide them.

00:40:07.136 --> 00:40:42.280
The Lord says, 'There is no bunker that will hide them, for the day of wrath has come.

00:40:42.280 --> 00:40:54.240
' As I look into it, I see these massive angelic beings standing together.

00:40:55.238 --> 00:41:10.998
They are transparent but holding trumpets, and they look like they have waterfalls or rain inside of them.

00:41:14.480 --> 00:41:19.448
They are in the east and look spooky.

00:41:19.448 --> 00:41:25.669
Their skin is light, but their interiors look like water vapor.

00:41:25.669 --> 00:42:08.755
I've never seen an angel look like this.

00:42:08.755 --> 00:42:10.124
They're blowing these horns.

00:42:13.093 --> 00:42:17.119
