00:43:41.005 --> 00:43:46.630
Everything is shaking violently.

00:43:46.640 --> 00:44:10.319
The earth will rock and reel like a drunkard.

00:44:46.960 --> 00:44:50.870
Glory to God, Diana.

00:44:53.097 --> 00:44:59.648
I'm just sitting here looking at all this, and He is allowing me to see it.

00:45:09.839 --> 00:45:12.474
It is the great and terrible day, and every knee will bow.

00:45:28.746 --> 00:45:48.950
