00:45:48.960 --> 00:45:55.990
I see these angels blowing their horns, and it's deafening.

00:46:01.580 --> 00:46:07.060
I see Mark Zuckerberg going down in his bunker, and his curly hair is a little thicker and poofier than usual.

00:46:09.230 --> 00:46:14.560
He's trembling at the sight of God and what he's seeing on his island.

00:46:17.320 --> 00:46:18.679
I see the volcanoes going off.

00:46:26.640 --> 00:46:27.090
This is about the love of money, a grotesqueness and infatuation with it.

00:46:41.200 --> 00:46:41.404
It's a stench to the Father.

00:46:41.404 --> 00:46:48.960
They're trembling in their caves and bunkers because no one will escape the wrath to come.

00:46:48.960 --> 00:46:54.877
You must know Him; you must know His Son.

00:46:54.877 --> 00:47:13.840
Oh Jesus, may we all fall in love more with You.

00:47:13.840 --> 00:47:17.743
